Did you try:

Solved with

sudo pip uninstall six
sudo pip install six --upgrade --target="/usr/lib/python2.7/dist-packages"

From: #2746

I had this problem at one point, can't remember how I solved it but often times the Linux related troubleshooting with TF can help on OS X.
